title: Frank Lloyd Wright Socks—Tree Of Life/Gray
description:
Sit back, relax, and put your feet up. Way up! You’ll want everyone to see this fancy footwear. Made of a soft and sturdy cotton, nylon and spandex blend, these socks are woven with a design adapted from Frank Lloyd Wright’s®(American, 1867–1959) Tree of Life Art Glass Window at the Darwin D. Martin House.  Designed in New York, produced in Columbia. 

3 ½ x 10 in.
